      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is used under a validated installation qualification protocol. Version-controlled solver settings files are archived in the project repository. Regression tests covering laminar pipe flow, rotating frame momentum, and scalar transport confirm solver correctness for the relevant physics. SQA level assessed as Gradation 2 compliant."
