      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation study conducted at the 5.0 L/min, 3500 RPM operating point (coarse: 4.2M cells, medium: 11.7M cells, fine: 28.4M cells). GCI for NIH on the medium mesh is 6.3%, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The medium mesh is adopted for all production simulations. Discretization error assessed as meeting required level."
    },
